text: Vieques (English pronunciation: vee-AY-kayz or -kez), in full Isla de Vieques, is an island-municipality of Puerto Rico in the northeastern Caribbean. Like mainland Puerto Rico the island is United States territory, though it retains strong Spanish influences from 400 years of Spanish ownership. ==References== ==Other websites== * Pictures from the island * Vieques, Puerto Rico: ATSDR Documents Dealing with the Isla de Vieques Bombing Range * Category:Municipalities of Puerto Rico
